CreateDistributionClerk is an ActionForm
    action is CreateDistributionClerkForEmployee
        on completion navigate to ViewDistributionClerk
    Layout
        single column
            HROrganization
                label is "Organization"
                display as text
            DistributionClerk
                label is "Employee"
                display as text
            Company
                label is "Company"
                select is DistributionManagementCompanySelectList
                display as required
